[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     2[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     3[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Complexity:** Complex · **Phase:** High-touch integration · **Estimated Cost:** ~$3-15 per active member per month (depends on patient acuity, integration depth, channel mix, model choice, RAG depth, and care-management-team handoff overhead)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     4[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
